word_group.brief_definition: 相同；完全一致；一模一样

bilingual.source: The twins wore identical outfits to the party.
bilingual.target: 双胞胎穿着完全相同的服装参加了聚会。

bilingual.source: She bought three identical outfits for her triplets.
bilingual.target: 她为她的三胞胎买了三套相同的衣服。

bilingual.source: The factory uses a special mould to produce identical parts.
bilingual.target: 工厂使用特殊的模具生产相同的零件。

bilingual.source: During mitosis, the cell divides into two identical daughter cells.
bilingual.target: 在有丝分裂过程中，细胞分裂成两个相同的子细胞。

bilingual.source: Scientists use a replicator to create identical samples for testing.
bilingual.target: 科学家使用复制器来创建相同的测试样本。

bilingual.source: The process of cloning involves creating a genetically identical copy.
bilingual.target: 克隆过程涉及创建一个基因完全相同的副本。

bilingual.source: The two devices are functionally identical despite their different designs.
bilingual.target: 尽管设计不同，这两种设备在功能上是相同的。

bilingual.source: Identical twins have the same genotype but can have different phenotype.
bilingual.target: 同卵双胞胎有相同的基因型，但可以有不同的表型。

bilingual.source: The material is isotropic, meaning it has identical properties in all directions.
bilingual.target: 这种材料是各向同性的，意味着它在所有方向上具有相同的特性。

bilingual.source: An idempotent HTTP method means that making multiple identical requests has the same effect as making a single request.
bilingual.target: 幂等的HTTP（HyperText Transfer Protocol，超文本传输协议）方法意味着多次相同的请求与单次请求具有相同的效果。

yingyinNormal.en: It's a gene. Well, it's sort of two genes, but two genes that are identical.
yingyinNormal.zh: 基因问题。是两种基因。完全相同的基因。

yingyinNormal.en: What? My identical hand twin. What's an identical hand twin?
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么？我的双胞手啊！什么是双胞手？

yingyinNormal.en: It's impossible. Why? Two people can't have identical DNA.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是不可能的。怎么了？两个人的DNA不可能完全相同。

yingyinNormal.en: What's it sound like? It's a guy with my identical hands.
yingyinNormal.zh: 听起来像什么？ 有个人的手跟我一模一样。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey. Phoebe. Yeah. I found my identical hand twin. Oh, you're so lucky.
yingyinNormal.zh: 菲比，我找到我的双胞手了！你真幸运。

yingyinNormal.en: A cold fusion of two universal elements, identical in weight, equal in force.
yingyinNormal.zh: 两个通用元素冷聚变，重量一致，力量均等。

yingyinNormal.en: Chandler. You are not gonna believe this. I have found my identical hand twin.
yingyinNormal.zh: 钱德，说了你一定不相信，我找到我的双胞手了！

yingyinNormal.en: The physics is almost identical to the stable orbits of planets, satellites, and moons.
yingyinNormal.zh: 其中的物理作用和星球、人造卫星以及月亮所运行的稳定轨道相似程度极高。

yingyinNormal.en: Stop. Put up 4847 and 2181 side-by-side. They're identical. Translate. A boy and a girl.
yingyinNormal.zh: 停。将4847号2181号进行比较。完全相同。导出基因信息。一男一女。

yingyinNormal.en: They're identical. Now, I've never seen anything like that in the business world. Stop it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一个模子刻出来的，我在商界做了这么久，从来没看过这种事。别再说了。

yingyinNormal.en: How? Look, I don't have it all worked out yet, but it's gotta mean big money. Come on. Identical hands.
yingyinNormal.zh: 怎么变？我还没有完全想出来，不过保证很有赚头，拜托，一模一样的手耶！

yingyinNormal.en: Wouldn't you pay good money to see these identical hands showcased in some type of a entertainment venue?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你愿不愿意花大钱去看手掌一模一样的两个人这种娱乐性的演出？

yingyinNormal.en: With my vitamins, my melatonin sleep patches, my bio-identical estrogen cream, progesterone cream, a touch of testosterone.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有了我的维他命，褪黑素睡眠膏，生物雌性激素霜，黄体酮膏，还有一点睾丸素。

yingyinNormal.en: Identical busts? Yeah, and this one to a Dr Barnicot in Holborn. Three in total. God knows who'd want to do something like this.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一样的半身像吗？对，这是霍尔本的一位巴尼科特博士的。一共三个，天知道谁会做这种事。

yingyinNormal.en: I've got everything masked. The algorithms for ICO and the campaign are identical. It's just a matter of what variables you input.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我把一切都掩盖好了，监控哈里发国和竞选采用的算法完全相同，只是输入的变量不一样而已。

yingyinNormal.en: No. No. I support you 100%. I just didn't, I didn't get it right away. You know now I'm caught up. Identical hand twins. It's a million-dollar idea.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，我百分之百支持你，只是我一时没回过神来，我现在懂了，双胞手！这点子值上百万。

yingyinNormal.en: In fact the benefit of the national brands over the store brands were identical to the advantage of the national brands over the discounted national brands.
yingyinNormal.zh: 事实上所谓的名牌药物的疗效优势相比于普通品牌药物，就好比于全价药和打折药物在治疗疗效上的区别。

yingyinNormal.en: The flags of Liechtenstein and Haiti were identical by coincidence, a fact that wasn't discovered until they competed against each other at the 1936 Olympics.
yingyinNormal.zh: 列支敦斯登和海地的国旗以前碰巧是一样的，直到两国在1936年奥运会对战时才发现这个巧合。

yingyinNormal.en: A new nautilus puzzle has appeared that is nearly identical to the very first one I encountered, down to a phone number that decodes to a set of GPS coordinates.
yingyinNormal.zh: 鹦鹉螺谜题出现了，非常像我之前碰到的那个，一个手机号码，可以解码为GPS坐标。

yingyinNormal.en: We grabbed him in transit just as he was logging out of the OASIS, so he thinks he's back in his office in the real world. But actually, he's here, in the identical office that Aech built.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他正准备从绿洲下线时我们抓住了他，所以他以为自己回到了现实世界的办公室。但其实他在艾奇建造的，一模一样的虚拟办公室里。
